{"tid":1296736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線：議員批警員執勤沒出示委任證","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:00:11.000Z","uid":90232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"802302c7fa67e0fc3438747e89245b0ee48bd3a9","tid":1296736,"uid":90232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"【記協、攝記協譴責警方 旺角清場喝罵、推撞記者】<br />\n【議員批警員執勤沒出示委任證】<br />\n<br />\n記者協會及攝影記者協會發出聯合聲明，嚴厲譴責警方在旺角清場期間，喝罵及推撞記者。<br />\n<br />\n有議員亦批評，有警員執勤時沒有出示委任證，以及用過分武力對待示威者。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #記協 #攝記協 #譴責 #警方 #旺角 #清場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2358200164398416/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2358200164398416%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpRQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=1f1c7a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2358200164398416/</a>"},{"pid":"27de675814dde9f694f49e5f40f521d37009c58c","tid":1296736,"uid":90232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"【旺角清場】<br />\n【警方推進與記者發生推撞全程】<br />\n<br />\n7月7日警方於旺角清場，至深夜12時許，立法會議員譚文豪及區諾軒到達彌敦道及登打士街交界，要求與警方的指揮官對話。及後警方向前推進，與記者發生推撞。推進行動至近咸美頓街，警方傳媒聯絡組到場為止，全程歷時約五分鐘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2495701323813617/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2495701323813617%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpRQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=6d06d273\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2495701323813617/</a>"},{"pid":"b558ea5c2928d04a3befa5cd3156d71df8dca249","tid":1296736,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"}]}